What you'll need to compile/use the package:

Using the package:
	An X server
	libcairo2, libx11
	The xsetbg binary
	The discover package

Compiling binaries:
	all: gcc
	write-message: libcairo2-dev libx11-dev

Patching packages:
	debian-like:
		libx11: "apt-get build-dep libx11-6"
		Xephyr: "apt-get build-dep xserver-xephyr"
		fakeroot
		dpkg

Packaging stuff:
	ubuntu:
		dpkg

Debian/Ubuntu users do this:
$ apt-get source xserver-xephyr
$ apt-get source libx11-6
$ apt-get install libcairo2 libcairo2-dev libx11-dev xloadimage discover
